Source.Name: rawtherapee
Source.Summary: A powerful cross-platform raw photo processing program
Source.Description: RawTherapee is an advanced cross-platform program for developing raw photos and for processing non-raw photos. It is non-destructive, makes use of OpenMP, supports all the cameras supported by dcraw and more, and carries out its calculations in a high precision 32-bit floating point engine.
